),(308,1,'2012-05-05 18:49:07','2012-05-05 22:49:07','<iframe src=\"http://www.amazon.com/s/?_encoding=UTF8&redirect=true&keywords=Arturo%20Mayorga&tag=artumayodotco-20&linkCode=ur2&camp=1789&rd=1&creative=390957&rh=n%3A163856011%2Cn%3A%21624868011%2Ck%3AArturo%20Mayorga%2Cp_n_feature_browse-bin%3A625150011\"></iframe>\r\n<div style=\"height: 109px; left: 137px; position: absolute; top: 260px; width: 526px; z-index: 1; background-color: black; opacity: 0\">\r\n\r\n<div id=\"img1\" style=\"left: 20px; position: absolute; top:15px; height: 80px; width: 80px;\"/>\r\n<img src=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/refdp_image_0.jpeg\" style=\"witdh: 100%; height: 100%\" usemap=\"#map1\"/>\r\n<map id=\"map1\" name=\"map1\">\r\n<area title=\"Lucid Dreams\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href); return false;\" onkeypress=\"window.open(this.href); return false;\" coords=\"0, 0, 200, 200\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Lucid-Dreams/dp/B007PW0P42\" alt=\"http://www.amazon.com/Lucid-Dreams/dp/B007PW0P42\" /></map>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"img2\" style=\"green; left: 110px; position: absolute; top:15px; height: 80px; width: 80px;\" onclick=\"window.open(\'\');\" >\r\n<img src=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/refdp_image_0-1.jpeg\" style=\"witdh: 100%; height: 100%\" usemap=\"#map2\"/>\r\n<map id=\"map2\" name=\"map2\">\r\n<area title=\"Cascades\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href); return false;\" onkeypress=\"window.open(this.href); return false;\" coords=\"0, 0, 200, 200\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B002CVNSRM\" alt=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B002CVNSRM\" /></map>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"q1\" style=\"top: 15px; left: 200px; width: 315px; height: 80px; font-size:50%\"> \r\n<br>\"The positive upbeat piano movements seem to sweep you off your feet at critical moments, leaving you breathless at the finish\"\r\n<br>-<a href=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=245\">John P. Olsen</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"q2\" style=\"top: 15px; left: 200px; width: 315px; height: 80px; font-size:50%\"> \r\n<br>\"Arturo is very successful by engraving a full range of emotional content and movement into his classic orchestra style music\"\r\n<br>-<a href=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=245\">John P. Olsen</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"q3\" style=\"top: 15px; left: 200px; width: 315px; height: 80px; font-size:50%\"> \r\n<br>\"While judging this debut album for myself, I became aware that the 10 songs of varying moods left me feeling they were a personal revelation of his emotional thoughts put to music.\"\r\n<br>-<a href=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=245\">John P. Olsen</a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"q4\" style=\"top: 15px; left: 200px; width: 315px; height: 80px; font-size:50%\"> \r\n<br>\"\'Cascades\' is a strong and promising first album from Arturo Mayorga, a musician who obviously loves what he\'s doing\"\r\n<br>-<a href=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=103\">Kathy Parsons</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"q5\" style=\"top: 15px; left: 200px; width: 315px; height: 80px; font-size:50%\"> \r\n<br>\"Debut albums can have an element of excitement, and Cascades has just that. A fine offering.\"\r\n<br>-<a href=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=253\">Mark Maxwell Abushady</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"q6\" style=\"top: 15px; left: 200px; width: 315px; height: 80px; font-size:75%\"> \r\n<br>\"a fine album of original piano compositions in a gentle, melodic and romantic style\"\r\n<br>-<a href=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=253\">Mark Maxwell Abushady</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"q7\" style=\"top: 15px; left: 200px; width: 315px; height: 80px; font-size:75%\"> \r\n<br>\"cohesive in their cleanly melodic style and superb execution.\"\r\n<br>-<a href=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=253\">Mark Maxwell Abushady</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"q8\" style=\"top: 15px; left: 200px; width: 315px; height: 80px; font-size:75%\"> \r\n<br>\"Cascades - Top 22 New Age Record of 2009\"\r\n<br>-<a href=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=269\">ZoneMusicReporter.com</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"q9\" style=\"top: 15px; left: 200px; width: 315px; height: 80px; font-size:50%\"> \r\n<br>\"When you listen to the strings supporting his keyboard on the opener, \'Sunrise\', you\'ll fall in love with his talent\"\r\n<br>-<a href=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=273\">Rotcod Zzaj</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"q10\" style=\"top: 15px; left: 200px; width: 315px; height: 80px; font-size:75%\"> \r\n<br>\"What an apt description for the beautiful music Arturo has created for your ears and your spirit.\"\r\n<br>-<a href=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=273\">Rotcod Zzaj</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<script type=\'text/javascript\' language=\"javascript\"> \r\nfadeCarousel([\"q1\",\"q2\",\"q3\",\"q4\",\"q5\",\"q6\",\"q7\",\"q8\",\"q9\",\"q10\"]);\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>','','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-40','','','2012-05-05 18:49:07','2012-05-05 22:49:07','',2,'http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=308',0,'revision','',0),(329,1,'2012-05-06 00:02:59','2012-05-06 04:02:59','<div id=\"video-catalog\">\r\n<table style=\"border-style: none;\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"border-style: none;\">\r\n<td style=\"border-style: none;\"><a title=\"Lucid Dreams  Teaser\" href=\"http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=142\">Lucid Dreams - Teaser</a>\r\n<iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/yb-zxYBKzC4\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"210\" height=\"136\"></iframe></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>','Video','','inherit','open','open','','24-revision-46','','','2012-05-06 00:02:59','2012-05-06 04:02:59','',24,'http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=329',0,'revision','',0),(330,1,'2012-05-05 21:09:46','2012-05-06 01:09:46','<div id=\"content-right\">Arturo is a composer/producer born in El Paso TX. Though he showed an aptitude for music at an early age, Arturo was encouraged to pursue alternate careers, and develop his music at his own pace. Throughout the years, he cultivated his gift and established his own approach to piano and musical composition.In 2009, after much encouragement from his colleagues, Arturo released his debut album Cascades. Cascades debuted on the NAR World New Age charts on position number 3 which led to licensing and placement deals of several tracks. Today, Arturo resides in NYC where he is active in the music community, and continues to explore his music and composition.</div>','Biography','','inherit','open','open','','30-revision-26','','','2012-05-05 21:09:46','2012-05-06 01:09:46','',30,'http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=330',0,'revision','',0),(331,1,'2012-05-05 21:10:13','2012-05-06 01:10:13','<div id=\"content-left\">Contact</div>\r\n<div>Direct:<a title=\"mailto:Arturo@ArturoMayorga.com?subject=[direct]\" href=\"mailto:Arturo@ArturoMayorga.com?subject=%5Bdirect%5D\">Arturo@ArturoMayorga.com</a></div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/pages/Arturo-Mayorga/103374001890\"><img id=\"shapeimage_1\" style=\"border: none; height: 36px; width: 38px; z-index: 1;\" src=\"/Home/Contact_files/shapeimage_1.png\" alt=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://arturomayorga.tumblr.com/\"><img id=\"shapeimage_2\" style=\"border: none; height: 36px; width: 96px; z-index: 1;\" title=\"\" src=\"/Home/Contact_files/shapeimage_2.png\" alt=\"\" usemap=\"#map2\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/arturosmusic\"><img style=\"border: none; height: 36px; width: 39px; z-index: 1;\" src=\"http://arturomayorga.com/Home/Contact_files/shapeimage_3.png\" alt=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.myspace.com/arkturusm\"><img id=\"shapeimage_4\" style=\"border: none; height: 36px; width: 43px; z-index: 1;\" title=\"\" src=\"/Home/Contact_files/shapeimage_4.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>','Contact','','inherit','open','open','','36-revision-25','','','2012-05-05 21:10:13','2012-05-06 01:10:13','',36,'http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=331',0,'revision','',0),(20,1,'2012-04-24 16:48:15','2012-04-24 20:48:15','[embed light]http://open.spotify.com/artist/5MBFPYFZTCfMdouSTn4Tht