ouraged to pursue alternate careers, and develop his music at his own pace. Throughout the years, he cultivated his gift and established his own approach to piano and musical composition.</p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0pt;\">In 2009, after much encouragement from his colleagues, Arturo released his debut album Cascades. Cascades debuted on the NAR World New Age charts on position number 3 which led to licensing and placement deals of several tracks. Today, Arturo resides in NYC where he is active in the music community, and continues to explore his music and composition.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n...','Biography','','inherit','open','open','','30-revision-21','','','2012-05-03 19:31:32','2012-05-03 23:31:32','',30,'http://arturomayorga.com/site/?p=241',0,'revision','',0),(242,1,'2012-05-02 20:40:42','2012-05-03 00:40:42','<script type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"javascript\">// <![CDATA[\r\ndocument.getElementById(\'wrapper\').style.background = \"#041a2c\";\r\ndocument.getElementById(\'name-banner\').style.backgroundImage = \"url(http://arturomayorga.com/Home/Music_files/backgroundimage_1.png)\";\r\ndocument.getElementById(\'wrapper\').style.backgroundImage = \"url(http://arturomayorga.com/Home/Music_files/backgroundimage_2.jpeg)\";\r\n// ]]></script>\r\n<div id=\"id9\" class=\"style_SkipStroke_5 stroke_0\" style=\"left: 115px; position: absolute; top: 10px; z-index: 1;\">[html5mp3full:161]</div>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"height: 109px; left: 137px; position: absolute; top: 260px; width: 526px; z-index: 1; background-color: black; opacity: 0.75;\">\r\n\r\n<script type=\'text/javascript\' language=\"javascript\"> // <![CDATA[\r\nfunction carous